            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/978868d5b1324e00/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-978868d5b1324e00-9ce61e twpub-978868d5b1324e00-6f4644 twpub-978868d5b1324e00-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c25\"><div class=\"c2\">While we cannot and do not solicit contributions from states where we have not met the solicitation requirements, we know of no prohibition against accepting unsolicited donations from donors in such states who approach us with offers to donate.</div></div></div>"
